{"tid":2352270,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博：「3桶油」或成美除牌目標","createTime":"2021-01-04T02:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T09:55:11.000Z","uid":185631,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"30ff495c83602032d5c87161ddeec6f3e7d17ee1","tid":2352270,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:24:09.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】紐交所上周五（1日）公布，因應美國總統特朗普行政命令，勒令三大中資電訊股在當地退市，彭博研究（Bloomberg Intelligence）發表報告指，美國下一步或會指向三大中資石油股要求其除牌，其中中海油（0883）更已被美國列為與軍方相關企業。<br />\n<br />\n或限制投資規模指數權重<br />\n中移動（0941）、中電信（0728）及聯通（0762）遭紐交所勒令除牌，根據聲明，三間公司預將於周四（7日）至下周一（11日）停牌，安排除牌事宜。<br />\n<br />\n彭博行業研究分析師Henik Fung認為，石油股可能成為下一目標，其中除中海油本身已被美方界定為軍方相關企業外，石油作為重要軍事戰略資源，亦極有可能成為下一輪針對目標。<br />\n<br />\n他指，目前美國投資者持有的中海油、中石油（0857）及中石化（0386）股票，市值約104億美元（約811.2億港元）。他估計，針對措施除了除牌外，亦可能限制美國投資者投資中資股規模，以及限制中資股在重要指數的權重。<br />\n<br />\nHenik Fung進一步指出，現時MSCI正就美國列為軍方相關企業的處理進行研究，可能會被剔出，富士羅素亦在進行同類檢討。<br />\n<br />\n他估計，中海油一旦被剔出MSCI中國指數，約市值23億美元（約179.4億港元）股份將會被拋售，倘三大中資石油股全被剔出，拋售股份市值規模更高達48億美元（約374.4億港元）。"},{"pid":"7c88f5db341c7ee1b3e8a41b2b55cc38d6d9f7b8","tid":2352270,"uid":49784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:27:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eac3e3e6bf8b80be4e4a1d8c155453646890d471","tid":2352270,"uid":49784,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:27:31.000Z","msg":"連環拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89c4467ed685398e40629c5f6c3f55aa63569b3a","tid":2352270,"uid":253499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:29:24.000Z","msg":"Put咗883，call咗3690"},{"pid":"47a1c33ca08b6d0b917e32ba01b5ceba72c014cc","tid":2352270,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e08e3d6e09ebfb87fd647b36dcd1d814becca40a","tid":2352270,"uid":29153,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:23:48.000Z","msg":"基本上所有大陸公司都係有軍方背景，大陸要你幫手既時侯，邊有得say no"},{"pid":"8fe8f33b890835d4e8ec0e1b02085dd09e0a4859","tid":2352270,"uid":26708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e08e3d6e09ebfb87fd647b36dcd1d814becca40a","tid":2352270,"uid":29153,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:23:48.000Z","msg":"基本上所有大陸公司都係有軍方背景，大陸要你幫手既時侯，邊有得say no"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohyes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以要全部除牌退市"},{"pid":"2c34b3b754f18553a6a7b37a0aeff678d29198b8","tid":2352270,"uid":340088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:25:36.000Z","msg":"香港又升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e9e33f6f225d01d1b2f372bda423a994cabe53","tid":2352270,"uid":110568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89c4467ed685398e40629c5f6c3f55aa63569b3a","tid":2352270,"uid":253499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T02:29:24.000Z","msg":"Put咗883，call咗3690"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:40:03.000Z","msg":"你咁買係跟麵神定自己？"},{"pid":"75aa3b26296f9207bceab61d1d2f3fea8e8725be","tid":2352270,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:52:30.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2e25b572c54a97dac49e48eac95df0d45487a4ca","tid":2352270,"uid":39010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"咁計跟本中國全部公司都有共黨背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部唔洗做了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602373e429a3a7044454b4fe246586547d541646","tid":2352270,"uid":68620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T09:55:11.000Z","msg":"驚茜<br />\n有香港依個假國際市場<br />\n要cup水話咁易"}]}